headline: Lennox International (LII) Advances Digital Transformation With AI Tools For HVAC Technicians And Homeowners
summary: Lennox International (LII) is actively integrating AI technology into its services with the recent rollout of its Technical Support AI Agent, designed to assist HVAC technicians more efficiently. Over the past week, LII's stock price rose by 2.5%, a movement that aligns with the general market uptick but slightly outpaces the market's 1.4% gain.
